in";s:4:"text";s:15:"haha ok thanks!";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1427322253";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#eef2b4";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14273222533";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f4c7f6";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1305891;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1305891";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Dolly";s:4:"text";s:1863:"52nd &amp; Mane [br]The building and restaurant is called 52nd &amp; Mane. Standing three stories tall it was one of the larger structures to be found downtown. As for it&#039;s name it was to represent both the famous strip of road in downtown Manehatten and Mane street, the road that this building is situated on. The main room is a large lavish space decorated with white and black painted walls, silver and black marble counter tops, and maroon draperies, lamp shades, and seat cushions. On the walls are many poster sized black and white pictures of famous landmarks of Manehatten including Rockefilly plaza, Canter Park, Barnway, The Empire Stable, and various others. There are also pictures of very personal and beautiful spaces found around Ponyville, it&rsquo;s as if Joe is trying to marry the two cities using pictures under this one roof. As for the lounge area there are many available seating spaces including tables for up to six ponies, booth spaces along the walls that can sit four comfortably and of course a long bar against the far wall of this open space. The bar usually has three to five ponies who serve all kinds of wonderful beverage choices, including MojitoJoe brand sodas on tap, specialty house soda drinks, floats, lemonade, ciders, teas (hot/cold) and exclusively sold by the bottle Sweet Apple Cider, a sparkling cider fit for the princesses. The first two floors have space for a stage where live music, floor shows and other such performers can entertain guests. In the back of this lounge space is a small but well designed kitchen, here a small team of chefs prepare quick and tasty meals specializing in grilled and deli meals including The Reuben Garden Sandwich, Roasted Colty Island Hot Peppers, Baked Macaroni Spinach and Cheese, and for desert and coming straight from Manehatten herself, Manehatten style cheesecake.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1427323063";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14273230655";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1305894;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1305894";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11936";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Dolly";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1310";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:10:"thank you!";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1427323880";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#eef2b4";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14273238800";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f4c7f6";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1305895;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1305895";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Dolly";s:4:"text";s:11:"No problem!";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1427323892";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14273238944";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1305901;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1305901";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11936";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Dolly";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1310";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:58:"sorry one last question, what floor are all of you on? heh";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1427324410";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#eef2b4";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14273244106";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f4c7f6";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1305909;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1305909";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s: